<div class="container">
    <div class="hero" style="padding: 2rem 0;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Get In Touch</h1>
        <p>Let's start a conversation about your next project</p>
    </div>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Me a Message
            </h2>
            <form action="#" method="POST" style="width: 100%;">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i> Full Name
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Your full name">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email Address
                    </label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your.email@example.com">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="subject">
                        <i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Subject
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required placeholder="What's this about?">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">
                        <i class="fas fa-comment"></i> Message
                    </label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required placeholder="Tell me about your project or idea..."></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn" style="width: 100%;">
                    <i class="fas fa-send"></i> Send Message
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
            <div class="card">
                <h2 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Contact Information
                </h2>
                
                <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                        <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope" style="color: white;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Email</h4>
                            <p style="color: #666; margin: 0;"><%= @profile[:email] %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                        <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone" style="color: white;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Phone</h4>
                            <p style="color: #666; margin: 0;"><%= @profile[:phone] %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                        <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 1rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="color: white;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Location</h4>
                            <p style="color: #666; margin: 0;"><%= @profile[:location] %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i> Social Media
                </h3>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="#" style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #667eea; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                        <i class="fab fa-github" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> GitHub
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #667eea; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> LinkedIn
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #667eea; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                        <i class="fab fa-twitter" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Twitter
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Response Time
                </h3>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    I typically respond to messages within 24 hours during weekdays. 
                    For urgent matters, feel free to reach out via phone.
                </p>
                
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Let's Collaborate
                </h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">
                    Whether you have a project in mind, need technical consultation, 
                    or just want to connect, I'd love to hear from you!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #667eea;">
            <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
            <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What's your typical project timeline?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666;">Project timelines vary depending on complexity, but most web applications take 2-8 weeks from concept to deployment.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Do you work on small projects?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666;">Absolutely! I enjoy working on projects of all sizes, from simple landing pages to complex enterprise applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What technologies do you specialize in?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666;">I specialize in Ruby on Rails, JavaScript (React, Node.js), and modern web technologies. I'm always learning new tools!</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Do you provide ongoing support?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666;">Yes! I offer maintenance and support packages to keep your applications running smoothly after launch.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container > div:first-child {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
            gap: 2rem !important;
        }
    }
</style>